descriptionHtml:
◈ ANTTIME ◈
The first T2E(Time-to-Earn) project that will make your time valuable.
Download the ANTTIME app now and join the production activities with your ant friends!

■ APP Introduction
Everyone has a fair share of time, are you getting value out of it?
Through ANTTIME, simply convert your time into an asset with just a few clicks.
Your ants will eagerly engage in production activities on your behalf.

1. TIME-TO-EARN: Mine coins every hour with just a single click.
2. REFERRAL BOOST: More friends, more efficient TIME production.
3. TIME WALLET: Transfer TIME Points through TIME Blockchain.
